----==== ZE FRANK RIDES AGAIN ====----

These scripts generate an Atom feed for The Show with Ze Frank[1], time-shifted
4 years[2].

I am providing a public feed at
    http://joe.definitelynotsafe.com/ze-frank-rides-again.atom
to which you are welcome to subscribe.

----==== USAGE ====----

$ ./todaysshow.rb
    <entry>
        <title>The Show for Friday, Mar 17</title>
        <link href="http://www.zefrank.com/theshow/archives/2006/03/031706.html"/>
        <author><name>Ze Frank</name></author>
        <id>tag:joe.definitelynotsafe.com,2010-03-19:/zefrank/031706</id>
        <updated>2010-03-21T15:43:09-07:00</updated>
        <summary>jessica simpson loves bush, neverland, iraqis buy fruit, google scalia, bill gates, one laptop per child, 
origami</summary>
    </entry>

